Local:
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
------------------------------------
On AWS EC2 / Render (basic idea):

Create EC2 instance (with GPU if model is big, or use HF Inference API instead).

Install Python + requirements.

Use uvicorn + nginx or just a managed platform (Render/ Railway).

Optionally add Streamlit for internal UI (streamlit run app/ui_streamlit.py).
